title: WHS announces second trimester honor rolls
title_page: WHS announces second trimester honor rolls
maintext:
The high honor roll and regular honor roll for the second trimester of the 2017-18 academic year have been announced at Watertown High School.
A student must be enrolled in a minimum of four (class of 2018, 2019, 2020) or five (class of 2021) classes to qualify for high honor roll of 3.67 and higher and at least a 3.2-3.669 for honors.
